Study_Name: Watershed Friendly Gardening Education Program-Water Quality Monitoring Study
Study_Purpose: The goal of the Water Quality Monitoring Study was to assess the efficancy of the Watershed Friendly Gardening Education Program.  The intent of the program was to provide information on watershed friendly practices to residents in the Lake Whatcom and Lake Samish watersheds through media such as printed materials, videos, training of landscapers and retailers, and a demonstration landscape.
Ecology_Program_or_Other_Responsible_Ent: Ecy Water Quality Program, Northwest Region
Study_QA_Project_Plan_Description: A project QAPP was prepared by Herrera Environmental Consultants and approved by Ecology.
